<plot>Something is happening to Jim, something he can't explain. His life has hit a wall. He is alone, isolated, and withdrawn. The only place he feels safe is the remote Peel Church. But this place is no sanctuary, and it is changing Jim. He cannot sleep, and when he does, he walks. When Jim desperately pulls Sam back into his life for help, they discover together - sometimes a sleepwalker, should never be woken.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?501405</url></doc>
